title: Duo mid isn't actually a "thing"
body:
Sorry other bronzies, but i got mid first. I know you think it's a thing, but sadly, it's not. 

I mean, it'd be cool and all. 

But, i'm trying to get out of this elo. So you're just gunna have to take that SUPER BIG BRONZE brain of yours... and learn a different spot right quick!~
